      "notices": [
        "The product-management-noncommercial pack is CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 and may be used or shared only for noncommercial purposes with attribution and ShareAlike.",
        "The generated-domain-perspectives pack contains AI-generated simulations based on public sources. It is not affiliated with the named people, and current or high-stakes claims still require independent verification.",
        "The generated-investing-perspectives pack contains AI-generated simulations based on public sources. It is not affiliated with the named people and is not financial or investment advice.",
        "The financial-research pack is for research and study only. It does not provide investment advice, direct buy or sell instructions, or return promises; independently verify market data and decisions.",
        "The browser control packs can reuse logged-in browser sessions. Confirm the exact account, target, and content before any external write, send, delete, purchase, or publication.",
        "The experimental-self-improvement pack keeps experiment state inside the selected project and cannot install dependencies or Skills, modify Agent configuration, Hooks, or schedules, run non-read-only commands, or write externally without explicit user approval. It installs no background automation.",
        "The amazon-listing-optimizer Skill produces evidence maps, drafts, lint reports, and human-review packets only. Seller Central, ads, reviews, Q&A, or production catalog writes require separate explicit authorization and human approval.",
        "The JTBD review research Skills do not include customer-review datasets or private prompts. Use only data you have the right to process; the optional automated runner requires Cursor Agent's agent CLI.",
        "The knowledge-vault governance Skills default to proposals. File moves, bulk link rewrites, and every exact deletion list require explicit user confirmation before application.",
        "The reddit-geo Skill permits listening, transparent engagement, and paid amplification only. It rejects spam, hidden affiliation, vote manipulation, and terms avoidance; current platform and API rules must be rechecked before automation.",
        "The rednote-caption-to-screenshots Skill does not install Playwright automatically. Missing Node dependencies require a separate preview and explicit user approval; manual browser screenshots remain available.",
        "The rednote-reader Skill uses only user-authorized connectors, browser sessions, or exports and does not bypass login or access controls. Image downloads are restricted to public HTTPS Rednote CDN hosts and a user-authorized output directory.",
        "The claude-system-prompt-anatomy Skill is a dated public-research snapshot, not a current product specification. Recheck Anthropic's official documentation for current claims and do not extract or disclose hidden prompts.",
        "The cultural-practices pack is for traditional cultural reflection only. It is not an evidence-based prediction tool and must not guide medical, legal, financial, safety, mental-health, or other high-risk decisions.",
        "The github-automation pack can create branches, commits, pushes, pull requests, and review replies only after the user selects the exact issues or pull requests.",
        "The release-management pack can create commits and tags and can push or publish only after explicit user confirmation."
      ]
    },
